@fixtures

# mark a test with a label
@pytest.mark.[label]

# run tests with only that label
pytest -v -m [label]

# or except the ones with the label
pytest -v -m "not [label]"

# only run tests with test_[name]
pytest -k [test name]


@mark.parametrize()

# how to run pytest for specific test
$ pytest -k [name of python module]

-s  print all string output
-v  print names of individual tests as they run
-x  stop at first error
-k  run tests matching following keyword
